dence":["a reproducible Data Platform Design Doc pipeline with input, transformation, and output checks.","README or notes that explain setup, usage, assumptions, and expected output.","Pipeline run output, data-quality checks, and before/after records or tables.","Validation evidence such as tests, screenshots, logs, query results, metrics, traces, or review notes.","Short reflection on trade-offs, limitations, and one reasonable next improvement."],"reviewFocus":["Does the artifact directly match the project brief?","Can another person run, inspect, or review the result from the provided notes?","Are assumptions, limitations, and trade-offs stated clearly?"],"scopeGuardrails":["Keep the implementation focused on the stated project brief.","Prefer a complete small artifact over a broad unfinished system.","Treat completion as reviewable evidence, not a certification claim."],"claimLimit":"Completion creates reviewable project evidence. It does not certify mastery or guarantee job readiness.","evidenceRequired":true,"optionalPractice":false,"milestone":true,"source":"roadmap.sh/data-engineer","nodeKey":"proj-architecture-design-doc"}'::jsonb, true, true, '["Apply Data Engineering, Documentation through a focused Data Platform Design Doc artifact.","Explain the main design, data, tooling, workflow, or review decisions behind the project.","Validate the result with evidence that another person can inspect.","Document assumptions, limitations, and a concrete follow-up improvement."]'::jsonb, '["The a reproducible Data Platform Design Doc pipeline with input, transformation, and output checks is available for review.","The Data Platform Design Doc scope, setup path, input data or scenario, and expected output are documented.","The main workflow runs or can be inspected through a notebook, repository, dashboard, prototype, report, configuration, or case study.","Validation evidence is included and directly relates to the project brief.","The notes identify trade-offs, limitations, and one next improvement without claiming mastery or job readiness."]'::jsonb),
