('gate-final-review', 'ph-portfolio-career', 81, 'checkpoint', 'gate', NULL, NULL, 'Final Data Engineering Review Gate', 'Final roadmap checkpoint for Portfolio, Interview Readiness, and Capstone. The learner reviews portfolio evidence, unresolved gaps, and next learning priorities across the data engineering path.', 'This checkpoint closes the suggested data engineering orientation path by organizing evidence and next steps. It is not an employment guarantee or formal competency certification.', 'checkpoint', 'ph-portfolio-career-gates', 99, 81, 1, 'intermediate', 85, 300, 10030, '{"checkpoint": true, "source": "roadmap.sh/data-engineer", "nodeKey": "gate-final-review", "checkpointPurpose": "phase_review", "reviewMode": "final_review", "evidenceRequired": true, "claimLimit": "orientation_and_progress_review_only_not_certification"}'::jsonb, true, true, '["Connect completed roadmap work to a coherent data engineering learning narrative.", "Review portfolio or project evidence and identify which artifacts are ready to share.", "Define remaining gaps and future specialization priorities."]'::jsonb, '["Summarize completed phases, projects, and major skill groups.", "Attach or reference portfolio evidence, project links, diagrams, reports, tests, or notes where available.", "List remaining gaps or specialization topics for future learning.", "State that the checkpoint is a planning review, not proof of job readiness."]'::jsonb),
('proj-capstone-data-platform', 'ph-portfolio-career', 91, 'project', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Required Data Engineering Capstone Project', 'Capstone project: Build a production-style data platform: ingestion, storage, orchestration, transformation, quality tests, warehouse/lakehouse tables, observability, docs, and deployment notes.', 'This project gives learners a concrete way to practice Portfolio, Interview Readiness, and Capstone by producing a portfolio-ready Data Engineering Capstone Project case study and integrated artifact. The artifact is intended for review and reflection, not as proof of mastery or job readiness.', 'checkpoint', 'ph-portfolio-career-projects', 100, 91, 16, 'advanced', 75, 700, 10060, '{"project":true,"projectBrief":"Build a production-style data platform: ingestion, storage, orchestration, transformation, quality tests, warehouse/lakehouse tables, observability, docs, and deployment notes.","projectKind":"portfolio_capstone","projectScope":"portfolio_capstone","projectPurpose":"Integrate several roadmap areas into a portfolio-ready case study.","phaseContext":"Portfolio, Interview Readiness, and Capstone","deliverable":"a portfolio-ready Data Engineering Capstone Project case study and integrated artifact","skillsToPractice":["Data Engineering","Documentation"],"suggestedSteps":["Define the Data Engineering Capstone Project scenario, target user or reviewer, and the specific Portfolio, Interview Readiness, and Capstone concepts it will demonstrate.","Choose a coherent product or case-study scenario that can integrate the strongest projects from the roadmap.","Define the architecture, data or workflow model, user path, and review evidence before implementation.","Build the core artifact end-to-end with scoped features rather than disconnected demos.","Add validation evidence appropriate to the role, such as tests, metrics, query checks, playtest notes, traces, screenshots, or incident notes.","Prepare a case study explaining decisions, trade-offs, limitations, and what would need further review for real deployment.","Package the repository or artifact so another person can reproduce or inspect the result.","Create a review checklist that connects the artifact to the relevant skills and roadmap segment.","Write a limitation and risk section so the project is presented as reviewable evidence, not a certification claim."],"expectedEvidence":["a portfolio-ready Data Engineering Capstone Project case study and integrated artifact.","README or notes that explain setup, usage, assumptions, and expected output.","Case study page or write-up that connects the artifact to role-relevant decisions and evidence.","Validation evidence such as tests, screenshots, logs, query results, metrics, traces, or review notes.","Short reflection on trade-offs, limitations, and one reasonable next improvement.","Architecture, review checklist, and limitation section suitable for portfolio discussion."],"reviewFocus":["Does the artifact directly match the project brief?","Can another person run, inspect, or review the result from the provided notes?","Are assumptions, limitations, and trade-offs stated clearly?"],"scopeGuardrails":["Keep the implementation focused on the stated project brief.","Prefer a complete small artifact over a broad unfinished system.","Treat completion as reviewable evidence, not a certification claim."],"claimLimit":"Completion creates reviewable project evidence. It does not certify mastery or guarantee job readiness.","evidenceRequired":true,"optionalPractice":false,"milestone":true,"source":"roadmap.sh/data-engineer","nodeKey":"proj-capstone-data-platform"}'::jsonb, true, true, '["Apply Data Engineering, Documentation through a focused Data Engineering Capstone Project artifact.","Integrate multiple roadmap areas into one coherent case study rather than isolated exercises.","Explain the main design, data, tooling, workflow, or review decisions behind the project.","Validate the result with evidence that another person can inspect.","Document assumptions, limitations, and a concrete follow-up improvement."]'::jsonb, '["The a portfolio-ready Data Engineering Capstone Project case study and integrated artifact is available for review.","The Data Engineering Capstone Project scope, setup path, input data or scenario, and expected output are documented.","The main workflow runs or can be inspected through a notebook, repository, dashboard, prototype, report, configuration, or case study.","The case study connects implementation decisions to relevant roadmap skills and explains why alternatives were not chosen.","Validation evidence is included and directly relates to the project brief.","The notes identify trade-offs, limitations, and one next improvement without claiming mastery or job readiness.","The project is packaged so a reviewer can understand the artifact without live mentoring."]'::jsonb),
('proj-portfolio-package', 'ph-portfolio-career', 92, 'project', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Required Portfolio Final Package', 'Capstone project: Polish the capstone with README, diagrams, runbook, data model docs, screenshots, sample queries, and known tradeoffs.', 'This project gives learners a concrete way to practice Portfolio, Interview Readiness, and Capstone by producing a portfolio-ready Portfolio Final Package case study and integrated artifact. The artifact is intended for review and reflection, not as proof of mastery or job readiness.', 'checkpoint', 'ph-portfolio-career-projects', 100, 92, 4, 'intermediate', 75, 700, 10140, '{"project":true,"projectBrief":"Polish the capstone with README, diagrams, runbook, data model docs, screenshots, sample queries, and known tradeoffs.","projectKind":"portfolio_capstone","projectScope":"portfolio_capstone","projectPurpose":"Integrate several roadmap areas into a portfolio-ready case study.","phaseContext":"Portfolio, Interview Readiness, and Capstone","deliverable":"a portfolio-ready Portfolio Final Package case study and integrated artifact","skillsToPractice":["Data Engineering","Documentation"],"suggestedSteps":["Define the Portfolio Final Package scenario and list the specific items to demonstrate: model behavior and evaluation.","Choose a coherent product or case-study scenario that can integrate the strongest projects from the roadmap.","Define the architecture, data or workflow model, user path, and review evidence before implementation.","Build the core artifact end-to-end with scoped features rather than disconnected demos.","Add validation evidence appropriate to the role, such as tests, metrics, query checks, playtest notes, traces, screenshots, or incident notes.","Prepare a case study explaining decisions, trade-offs, limitations, and what would need further review for real deployment.","Package the repository or artifact so another person can reproduce or inspect the result.","Create a review checklist that connects the artifact to the relevant skills and roadmap segment.","Write a limitation and risk section so the project is presented as reviewable evidence, not a certification claim."],"expectedEvidence":["a portfolio-ready Portfolio Final Package case study and integrated artifact.","README or notes that explain setup, usage, assumptions, and expected output.","Case study page or write-up that connects the artifact to role-relevant decisions and evidence.","Validation evidence such as tests, screenshots, logs, query results, metrics, traces, or review notes.","Short reflection on trade-offs, limitations, and one reasonable next improvement.","Architecture, review checklist, and limitation section suitable for portfolio discussion."],"reviewFocus":["Does the artifact directly match the project brief?","Can another person run, inspect, or review the result from the provided notes?","Are assumptions, limitations, and trade-offs stated clearly?"],"scopeGuardrails":["Keep the implementation focused on the stated project brief.","Prefer a complete small artifact over a broad unfinished system.","Treat completion as reviewable evidence, not a certification claim."],"claimLimit":"Completion creates reviewable project evidence. It does not certify mastery or guarantee job readiness.","evidenceRequired":true,"optionalPractice":false,"milestone":true,"source":"roadmap.sh/data-engineer","nodeKey":"proj-portfolio-package"}'::jsonb, true, true, '["Apply Data Engineering, Documentation through a focused Portfolio Final Package artifact.","Integrate multiple roadmap areas into one coherent case study rather than isolated exercises.","Explain the main design, data, tooling, workflow, or review decisions behind the project.","Validate the result with evidence that another person can inspect.","Document assumptions, limitations, and a concrete follow-up improvement."]'::jsonb, '["The a portfolio-ready Portfolio Final Package case study and integrated artifact is available for review.","The Portfolio Final Package scope, setup path, input data or scenario, and expected output are documented.","The main workflow runs or can be inspected through a notebook, repository, dashboard, prototype, report, configuration, or case study.","The case study connects implementation decisions to relevant roadmap skills and explains why alternatives were not chosen.","Validation evidence is included and directly relates to the project brief.","The notes identify trade-offs, limitations, and one next improvement without claiming mastery or job readiness.","The project is packaged so a reviewer can understand the artifact without live mentoring."]'::jsonb)
